Dear Setia

just edit the ?DESCRIPTION? file.

For maintainers, note the CRAN Repository Policy at http://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/policies.html which I think we generally also apply in Bioconductor: "The package?s DESCRIPTION file must show both the name and email address of a single designated maintainer (a person, not a mailing list). That contact address must be kept up to date, and be usable for information mailed by the CRAN team without any form of filtering, confirmation "

See also http://www.bioconductor.org/developers/package-guidelines/#responsibilities
 
Wolfgang




