>> we're forced to use suppressWarnings() for that.
>>
>
> For that use case, nothing has changed, we've always had a warning and
> we still have it.
>
> With BioC 2.14:
>
>   > merge(Seqinfo("chr1"), Seqinfo("chr2"))
>   Seqinfo of length 2
