CHANGES IN VERSION 2.0.0

NEW FEATURES

    o Add mapCoords() and pmapCoords() as replacements for map() and pmap().

    o Add coercion from list to RangesList.

    o Add slice,ANY method as a convenience for slice(as(x, "Rle"), ...).

