> working with a genome that has 39 chromosomes.
> ## Currently the supported organism in GenomeInfoDb with the highest
> number is Canis familiaris with 38 autosomal chrs.
>> seqlevelsStyle('seq1')
> Error in seqlevelsStyle("seq1") :
