15   LGXV     15
16   LGVI     16
17  LGVII     17
18 LGVIII     18
19  LGXIX     19
20   Pltd   <NA>

## Guessing 'LGI' with the higher lvl function works
> seqlevelsStyle('LGI')
[1] "NCBI"

## Mapping from 'LGI' in 'NCBI' style to 'JGI2' style doesn't work
> mapSeqlevels('LGI', 'JGI2')
Error in mapSeqlevels("LGI", "JGI2") :
  supplied seqname style "JGI2" is not supported

